Tavatron growled softly. She had thought as much:

"I knew Optimus Primal, steller-cycles ago. He's the reason I defected." 
Tavatron sheathed her sword and jumped on a nearby boulder. The ark doors 
loomed in the distance.

"There's the base. It's not far now." Tavatron jumped down and did a quick 
scan of the area. Satisfied that there were no Preds around Tavatron began 
to walk towards the base.

"Why did you defect?"

(OOC: Tav has no knowledge of Dinobot prior to their first encounter. Just 
to make it a lil interesting!)
